---
title: Mexican Chicken Breast Stew with Cheese
description: We love Mexican Chicken Breast Stew and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-chicken-breast-stew-ed771960-816043ab.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/mexican-chicken-breast-stew-612f96469b8d8908b521f2ba-96754fdf.pdf
cuisine: Mexican
